<section class="closing-section">
  <div class="closing-box">
    <div class="closing-glow"></div>
    <span class="closing-hashtag">#همة_تحيي_الأمة</span>
    <h2 class="closing-title font-aligarh tracking-normal">الأثر الحقيقي يبدأ بقرار</h2>
    <p class="closing-desc">
      نحن لا ننتظر الفرص، نصنعها. ولا نطلب الإذن للتغيير، نبنيه بأيدينا.
      إذا كنت تحمل همّة حقيقية، فأنت منا.
    </p>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/g/1Dr3HbRRfk/" class="closing-cta">
      <span>انضم إلى بنيان</span>
      <svg class="shrink-0 -scale-x-100" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .closing-section {
    @apply max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16;
  }

  .closing-box {
    @apply relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-3xl px-8 py-16 md:px-16 md:py-20 text-center;
  }

  .closing-glow {
    @apply absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[300px] h-[300px] rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-10 bg-ngreen;
  }

  .closing-hashtag {
    @apply inline-block text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-black mb-8 border border-lime-500/20 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-lime-500/5;
  }

  .closing-title {
    @apply text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight;
  }

  .closing-desc {
    @apply text-zinc-600 leading-[1.8] mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto;
  }

  .closing-cta {
    @apply inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-ngreen text-black font-bold text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-lime-400 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(168,229,36,0.3)];
  }
</style>
